<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include('partials/head.ejs') %>

<body>

  <!-------------web banner/header--------------->
  <%- include('partials/banner.ejs') %>

  <main id="main">

    <!-- ======= Breadcrumbs ======= -->
    <div class="breadcrumbs about-container">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
          <h1 class="display-3">Blog</h1>
          <ol>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li>Blog</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><!-- End Breadcrumbs -->

    <!-- ======= Blogs ======= -->
    <section class="py-4">
      <div class="container px-3 px-lg-3">
        <div class="row clearfix justify-content-center">
          <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-12">

            <!-----single post------->
            <div class="card single_post">
              <div class="body">
                <div class="img-post">
                  <img class="d-block img-fluid" src="assets/img/bg-parallax.jpg" alt="First slide">
                </div>
                <h3><a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/2023/12/25/dog-cat-animal-shelter-adoption/">As the pandemic adoption boom cools, pet shelters overflow</a></h3>
                <p>A tough economic climate last year put a chill on animal adoptions. But though shelters are packed, the outlook is brightening.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="footerBlog">
                <div class="actions">
                  <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/2023/12/25/dog-cat-animal-shelter-adoption/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" target="_blank">Continue Reading</a>
                </div>
                        
                <ul class="stats">
                  <li><a href="javascript:void(0);">General</a></li>
                  <!-- <li><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="fa fa-heart">28</a></li>
                  <li><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="fa fa-comment">128</a></li> -->
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-----single post------->
            <div class="card single_post">
              <div class="body">
                <div class="img-post">
                  <img class="d-block img-fluid" src="assets/img/home-1.jpg" alt="First slide">
                </div>
                <h3><a href="https://animalfoundation.com/whats-going-on/blog/basic-necessities-proper-pet-care">The basic necessities of proper pet care</a></h3>
                <p>Proper pet care is the basis of responsible pet ownership. It is important when you adopt a pet to understand it is a lifetime commitment to a furry family member who depends on you for his or her health and well-being. </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="footerBlog">
                <div class="actions">
                  <a href="https://animalfoundation.com/whats-going-on/blog/basic-necessities-proper-pet-care" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" target="_blank">Continue Reading</a>
                </div>
                        
                <ul class="stats">
                  <li><a href="javascript:void(0);">General</a></li>
                  <!-- <li><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="fa fa-heart">28</a></li>
                  <li><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="fa fa-comment">128</a></li> -->
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

             <!-----single post------->
             <div class="card single_post" id="pet-adoption-checklist">
              <div class="body">
                <div class="img-post">
                  <img class="d-block img-fluid" src="assets/img/blog-1.jpg" alt="First slide">
                </div>
                <h3><a href="https://careyanimalhospital.com/blog/pet-adoption-cincinnati-oh/">Pet Adoption Checklist: Are You Ready for Your New Pet?</a></h3>
                <p>Are you thinking about welcoming a new pet into your home? Adopting a pet is a big decision and comes with a lot of responsibilities. In this blog, weâ€™ll guide you through some of the most important things you need to know before bringing a new furry companion into your life. From preparing your home to understanding the signs that you may not be ready yet, we want to help you make the best possible decision for yourself (and your potential new family member!). </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="footerBlog">
                <div class="actions">
                  <a href="https://careyanimalhospital.com/blog/pet-adoption-cincinnati-oh/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" target="_blank">Continue Reading</a>
                </div>
                        
                <ul class="stats">
                  <li><a href="javascript:void(0);">General</a></li>
                  <!-- <li><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="fa fa-heart">28</a></li>
                  <li><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="fa fa-comment">128</a></li> -->
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-----single post------->
            <div class="card single_post" id="furparent">
              <div class="body">
                <div class="img-post">
                  <img class="d-block img-fluid" src="assets/img/blog-2.jpg" alt="First slide">
                </div>
                <h3><a href="https://republicasiamedia.com/fur-parenting-101-a-guide-on-how-to-be-a-good-pet-parent/">Fur-parenting 101: A guide on how to be a good pet parent</a></h3>
                <p>In this article, republicasia talked to some fur-parents and an animal doctor to discuss the emergence of adopting pets, as well as some tips on how to be the best parent to these magical furballs of sunshine and happiness. </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="footerBlog">
                <div class="actions">
                  <a href="https://republicasiamedia.com/fur-parenting-101-a-guide-on-how-to-be-a-good-pet-parent/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" target="_blank">Continue Reading</a>
                </div>
                        
                <ul class="stats">
                  <li><a href="javascript:void(0);">General</a></li>
                  <!-- <li><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="fa fa-heart">28</a></li>
                  <li><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="fa fa-comment">128</a></li> -->
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <% if (blogs.length > 0) {%>
              <% blogs.forEach(blog => { %>
                <!-----single post------->
              <div class="card single_post">
                <div class="body">
                  
                  <h3><a href="blog-details.html"><%= blog.title %></a></h3>
                  <p><%= blog.body %></p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="footerBlog">
                  <div class="actions">
                    <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Continue Reading</a>
                  </div>
                          
                  <ul class="stats">
                    <li><a href="javascript:void(0);">General</a></li>
                    <!-- <li><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="fa fa-heart">28</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="fa fa-comment">128</a></li> -->
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
  
              <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
              There are no blogs to display
            <% } %>

            

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-------------footer--------------->
  <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>


  <!--------------scripts-------------->
  <%- include('partials/scripts.ejs') %>

</body>

</html>
